                  <color r="255" g="255" b="255">Class: Mammals <i>(Mammalia)</i><br/>Order: Elephants <i>(Proboscidea)</i><br/>Family: Elephants <i>(Elephantidae)</i><br/>Genus: <i>Loxodonta</i><br/>Species:<i>cyclotis</i></color>
